Paying it forward 🇧🇸
Founded by @_jazz3, the mission of the Jazz Chisholm Foundation (@jazzchisholmfdn) is to provide meaningful opportunities and to foster the wellbeing of young athletes and their families from high need communities in Florida and the Bahamas.

Our focus:
— Providing equipment and resources to youth baseball and softball leagues
—Incorporating financial literacy education into various programming activities
—Supporting mission-aligned nonprofit organizations

Visit www.jazzchisholmfoundation.org or tap the link in bio to learn more!
